metadata.name: The Meta Bucks UMI 1.0
metadata.description: The Meta Bucks UMI is the main membership pass to our ecosystem. It represents an anonymous web3 identity. Aimed to help keep personal data useful for our clients financial needs, while protecting and accelerating social life, keeping our communities data sacred, secure and scarce online and in the real world. PreSale Participants will be entered into a raffle to win a virtual reality headset and travel pack made by Oculus.
